lexity\\n   - Files compared line-by-line in condensation\\n   \\n3. **File I/O patterns**\\n   - Metadata written to disk, then read back during condensation\\n   - Could be cached in-memory\\n   \\n4. **Shadow branch operations**\\n   - Multiple git tree builds per PostCommit\\n   - Potential for optimization with tree caching\\n\\n---\\n\\nThis exploration is now complete. The logging infrastructure is well-designed, `LogDuration()` already exists and is in use, and clear performance measurement points have been identified throughout the strategy package.\"}],\"totalDurationMs\":103243,\"totalTokens\":86205,\"totalToolUseCount\":33,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":0,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":140,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":82758,\"output_tokens\":3307,\"server_tool_use\":{\"web_search_requests\":0,\"web_fetch_requests\":0},\"service_tier\":\"standard\",\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":140,\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0},\"inference_geo\":\"\",\"iterations\":[],\"speed\":\"standard\"}},\"sourceToolAssistantUUID\":\"455bfcc7-9ece-49a6-91a2-55e78c2700a9\"}\n{\"parentUuid\":\"61f6f4e0-d8db-4f14-a58f-39b4922c4507\",\"isSidechain\":false,\"userType\":\"external\",\"cwd\":\"/Users/pfleidi/entire/cli/.worktrees/performance-logging-investigation\",\"sessionId\":\"2d62938d-a5d3-4bac-9d0f-bf8056720e6d\",\"version\":\"2.1.63\",\"gitBranch\":\"performance-logging-investigation\",\"slug\":\"wiggly-weaving-crayon\",\"message\":{\"model\":\"claude-opus-4-6\",\"id\":\"msg_01RGpGx1xy6usJFAsQN1Yeav\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"id\":\"toolu_01UpL1XAsXdVPMYvQzBz4oHp\",\"name\":\"TaskUpdate\",\"input\":{\"taskId\":\"1\",\"status\":\"completed\"},\"caller\":{\"type\":\"direct\"}}],\"stop_reason\":null,\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":1,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":3697,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":41017,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":3697},\"o